Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.19,0:00:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.79,0:00:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在大家都静静睡下的夜晚\Nみんなが寝静まった夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.99,0:00:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从窗口眺望夜空的话\N窓から空を見ていると
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.69,0:00:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以看到很厉害的东西\Nとっても　すごいものを　見たんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.59,0:00:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大人们都笑者说\N大人は誰も笑いながら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.59,0:00:30.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我电视看太多了\Nテレビの見過ぎと言うけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.29,0:00:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是我绝对绝对\N僕は　絶対に絶対に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.99,0:00:36.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会说谎\N嘘なんか言ってない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.79,0:00:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不会用名为常识的眼镜\N常識と言う眼鏡で
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.19,0:00:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对我们的世界\N僕たちの世界は
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.59,0:00:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进行窥视\Nのぞけやしないのさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.59,0:00:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,忘记了梦想的\N夢を忘れた
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.59,0:01:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,古老的地球人啊\N古い地球人よ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.59,0:01:06.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.83,0:01:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好奇妙的感觉\N不思議な気持ち
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.93,0:01:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这不是动画 这不是动画\Nアニメじゃない　アニメじゃない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.53,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.13,0:01:24.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是真的\N本当のことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.10,0:01:33.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?叫做米查的那個大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.51,0:01:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為了保住小命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.14,0:01:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把戈圖那夥人引到亞加瑪來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.38,0:01:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然,戈圖又開MS來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.28,0:01:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,連姬娜也突然反抗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.84,0:01:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪面臨危機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.46,0:01:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,MS打鬥時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.09,0:01:51.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還得小心別傷害到亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.25,0:01:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼大家\n不想想我的辛苦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.74,0:01:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十七話 奪回頂部戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.52,0:02:22.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾美莉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.90,0:02:27.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,剛才他好像喊了艾美莉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.55,0:02:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長的單身生活太久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.74,0:02:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說的話很嚇人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.16,0:02:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是大人的常識阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.73,0:02:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛\n噓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.65,0:02:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也讓我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.28,0:03:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.90,0:03:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.56,0:03:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你們在這裏做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.25,0:03:05.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.39,0:03:09.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米查先生找你去MS甲板
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.51,0:03:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米查有叫你們\n來偷窺我的房間嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.93,0:03:20.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以,請出來阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.09,0:03:22.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係,別在意\n我不能不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.80,0:03:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米查先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.49,0:03:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有看到命令書嗎?艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.87,0:03:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,命令亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.50,0:03:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,單獨去攻擊亞古捷斯\n太強人所難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才叫拉比安羅茲\n改造亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.50,0:03:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你年紀一大把,別幻想好嗎?\n大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.64,0:03:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開動MS的是我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.80,0:03:42.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少年,別喪氣阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.95,0:03:44.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們有米加戰車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.21,0:03:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米加戰車?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.42,0:03:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.98,0:03:47.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米加戰車是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是MS,是火箭推進器之類的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.71,0:04:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是MS的交通工具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.81,0:04:03.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是助飛器之類的嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.73,0:04:04.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別開玩笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.78,0:04:06.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,機動能力差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.73,0:04:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是米加火箭與助飛器的合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.77,0:04:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦上有高性能的米加粒子炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.57,0:04:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還有三架MS高達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且還有新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人類?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你作戰的手法我就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.99,0:04:24.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛新型MS作戰很累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.20,0:04:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔也來試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.33,0:04:28.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必你說我也想試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是不可以的,米查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.63,0:04:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.86,0:04:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.52,0:04:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度先生?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你妹妹的是我聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.82,0:04:43.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜的事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.16,0:04:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太可憐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.64,0:04:47.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,破壞亞古捷斯時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令妹可能會受到波及吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.24,0:04:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜會受到波及?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.33,0:05:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莉娜!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.92,0:05:07.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.77,0:05:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不會讓莉娜死在亞古捷斯上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.57,0:05:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,冷靜下來,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這個你不必擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.90,0:05:18.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可以在\n摧毀亞古捷斯前救出莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.54,0:05:21.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是阿\n你忘記我們有三架高達嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.99,0:05:24.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說的也是,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.09,0:05:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用高達小隊先救出莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.06,0:05:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,之後再破壞亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.12,0:05:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒錯,少年,試試看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.92,0:05:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,我就來試了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.95,0:05:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.89,0:05:45.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不必再這裏用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.97,0:05:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不,太偉大了\n我好感動啊,捷度先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.86,0:05:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少年!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,槍口別對著我,米莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.95,0:06:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,討厭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.93,0:06:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度,這樣不好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.34,0:06:16.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達的油漆才剛塗好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.21,0:06:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,確定是亞加瑪沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.24,0:06:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,航道剛好重疊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.77,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,留在這裏待命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.98,0:06:56.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不出動嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.45,0:06:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當然是待在MS上等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達交給我應付好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.60,0:07:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我跟那個駕駛員有仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.74,0:07:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你還說那句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是來打MS戰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是來埋伏,埋伏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.20,0:07:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,擊沉亞加瑪的話\n哈曼大人會給我們勳章嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.08,0:07:20.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋,不可以擊沉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.97,0:07:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜大人會死的!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.71,0:07:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,當指揮官真累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.31,0:07:29.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最近我越來越有體會,真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.40,0:07:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你終於瞭解\n馬士文大人的辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.44,0:07:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太多嘴了\n是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.67,0:07:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡\n好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.34,0:07:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?\n前方有巨大垃圾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是被拋棄的殖民地嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.53,0:07:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是這個,就是這個,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.33,0:07:52.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以它為靶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以用來測試主炮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,測試?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.19,0:08:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了,就這麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.32,0:08:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作主炮測試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.45,0:08:10.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把引擎的一半動力轉送到主炮那裏\n瞭解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.01,0:08:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,油漆未干就應該
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.11,0:08:17.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,貼張紙給人知道嘛\n真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.43,0:08:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想救你妹妹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.67,0:08:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.29,0:08:30.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那麼,救我吧\n疑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.34,0:08:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帶我去亞古捷斯\n我就讓你帶走她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不相信你說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.55,0:08:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們在月月\n不是曾經很知心的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.67,0:08:42.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你就相信我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.60,0:08:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.09,0:08:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你又沒欠亞加瑪的恩情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.42,0:08:52.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是...我...也可以救救你走的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太懂事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.89,0:08:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就喜歡你這一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.80,0:09:00.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我還沒決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你就表明啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,YES? NO?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.80,0:09:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.18,0:09:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.50,0:09:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以聽她的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,臭小孩!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.84,0:09:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別背叛阿,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.68,0:09:17.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由於主炮發射試驗的關係\n開始節省艦內用電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.41,0:09:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在試驗結束前\n各部人員停止作業,完畢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.60,0:09:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,煩死了,我自己回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.66,0:09:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度會死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:30.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.08,0:09:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.90,0:09:41.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.38,0:09:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞古捷斯果然是壞蛋集團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.06,0:09:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.30,0:09:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奇怪...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.71,0:09:54.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被發現了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.46,0:09:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說話,你有口臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就打開艙口吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.60,0:10:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.08,0:10:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊,我快窒息了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.16,0:10:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,空氣外洩啊...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.83,0:10:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.85,0:10:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉姐姐,姬娜逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.81,0:10:23.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.05,0:10:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個波霸母牛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.79,0:10:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目標進入主炮射程了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.64,0:10:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那種大小,一炮就化成灰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,照計算應該是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.35,0:10:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能源60%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.52,0:10:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離發射還有60秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.01,0:10:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈哈哈...這椅子坐起來不錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.72,0:10:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮暫停發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.23,0:10:53.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.67,0:10:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就說應該把她關禁閉才對\n人手不足也不該用她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.72,0:11:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡,過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.93,0:11:04.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮不測試了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.72,0:11:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那個等一下再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.59,0:11:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准妨礙我,我要回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.69,0:11:19.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小子!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.63,0:11:20.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,休想逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.03,0:11:26.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別牽連小孩,姬娜\n捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.77,0:11:33.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把洗達還給我\n吵死了,可惡...可惡..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.38,0:11:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.64,0:11:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁這機會...ZZ高達完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,油漆還沒干阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.99,0:11:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.05,0:11:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.93,0:11:48.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達被抓走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.79,0:11:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我駕駛MK2去阻止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.71,0:11:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.43,0:11:56.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不開艙口我就自己打破
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.61,0:12:26.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算你想回家,也不該這麼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.35,0:12:29.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我體重很輕,也帶我去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.91,0:12:40.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些小戰機,是ZZ高達的一部份\n果然被發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾魯!別急燥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.54,0:12:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都跟在我後面過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.23,0:12:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要乖乖聽話\n瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這小鬼睡著還不忘礙我的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.72,0:13:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開前我就破壞\n亞加瑪的主炮當告別禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.07,0:13:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,姬娜想做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快擊落它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.31,0:13:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我們的戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.44,0:13:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在是敵機了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.13,0:13:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是懲罰你們對我的奴役差遣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.84,0:13:20.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.54,0:13:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡\n臭小鬼...好難過...放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.59,0:13:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想對亞加瑪做什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.86,0:13:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手,你也會有危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.41,0:13:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就開回去\n不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要我就不放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前方發現敵人MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.17,0:13:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.99,0:13:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有四架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?怎麼挑在這個時候!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉,駕駛高達MK2出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.51,0:13:59.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Z高達,你的動作太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有很多私事阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.67,0:14:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡駕駛Z高達,出動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.56,0:14:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人沒有船艦,只開MS過來嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.75,0:14:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艦長,這是個好機會\n用主炮解決他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.73,0:14:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對手是MS,不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.88,0:14:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,塔台人員都各就各位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,灑下彈幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.91,0:14:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不准讓敵人MS靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.33,0:14:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對,別讓敵人MS靠近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.24,0:14:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.14,0:14:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ZZ高達在哪裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.16,0:14:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼路!ZZ高達分散開來了\n在亞加瑪的後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.77,0:14:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在就擊落它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想攻擊亞加瑪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.48,0:14:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這些人想幹什麼?一直在逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也去亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.75,0:15:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這兩架MS交給你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.95,0:15:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若不是為了顧及姬娜大人\n我就能擊沉它了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.83,0:15:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打中了,我打的炮彈打中了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.82,0:15:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是嗎?掉下來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我\n回去亞加瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要回去,放手\n我叫你放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛\n你才該放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.90,0:15:38.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我喊一二三,一起放開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.01,0:15:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道嘛?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.18,0:15:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不相信你\n伊萊,包圍核戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.16,0:15:43.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼做?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.64,0:15:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前後包圍,直接合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這太亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辦的到嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.71,0:15:50.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.89,0:15:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達正在努力中\n現在正是大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.68,0:15:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.66,0:15:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼沒合體?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.73,0:16:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能是新戰術
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.81,0:16:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,趁這機會打死它們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.86,0:16:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不會太卑鄙了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.48,0:16:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想對我說教還早十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.80,0:16:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人來了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.26,0:16:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敵人?那不就是自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.05,0:16:22.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,洗達!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.94,0:16:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,遭了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.89,0:16:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是誰?戈圖嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.87,0:16:29.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.54,0:16:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手,我是姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.58,0:16:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也在,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.36,0:16:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,我們先合體\n你支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.17,0:16:46.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.10,0:16:51.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖,住手\n我在機上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.33,0:16:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你被我控制住了,求救也沒用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,核戰機過來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.70,0:17:02.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功了,是捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.71,0:17:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,來吧,合體\n好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.86,0:17:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做夢,去死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.65,0:17:20.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,操縱系統被切斷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.43,0:17:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我早叫你死心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.52,0:17:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戈圖,別攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.77,0:17:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,看到我打的信號就發射飛彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.39,0:17:30.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後脫離,由我主導合體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.85,0:17:31.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.50,0:17:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開始脫離!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.99,0:17:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.91,0:17:56.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,合體了嗎?\n好巨大的機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.32,0:17:57.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,變形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.51,0:18:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要逃嗎?隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你說法不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.99,0:18:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,應該說去跟其他人會合,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.53,0:18:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伊萊,冠武,你們還好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯,我們沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.40,0:18:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄準亞加瑪的引擎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.05,0:18:23.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,疑!?...不怕爆炸傷及姬娜大人嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.08,0:18:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下走輕一點就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.91,0:18:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,還是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.23,0:18:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,繞到側面,前面的炮擊手太強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.01,0:18:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞄準艦橋的側面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.89,0:18:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼無法\n像剛才那樣打中呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.81,0:18:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炮擊手,擊落前方的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有辦法打贏吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.42,0:18:47.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒打完不知道!\n艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.72,0:18:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尼路,去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.74,0:18:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.23,0:18:57.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一下\n竟然還有MS在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.42,0:19:00.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,離開,這個角度危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.49,0:19:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,關閉艙口,被靠近就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.12,0:19:08.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要瞄準阿,尼路!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.69,0:19:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隊長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.30,0:19:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你逃不掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.54,0:19:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?是MS嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是?\n什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.88,0:19:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是邱貝雷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.13,0:19:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你認識那MS嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.77,0:19:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是哈曼艦的專用機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.02,0:19:42.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?主炮,用主炮打下它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米查先生,我才是指揮官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,請你閉嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.06,0:20:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.21,0:20:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪,快收容核戰機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.83,0:20:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那邊有東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.27,0:20:19.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.68,0:20:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.66,0:20:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可惡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.56,0:20:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.80,0:20:40.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是浮游炮的攻擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.37,0:20:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,駕駛員可能是新人類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:42.00,0:20:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼,是哈曼阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.25,0:20:47.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主炮準備發射\n周圍的高達快撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.78,0:20:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.31,0:20:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亞加瑪,快支援\n這次敵人很難纏!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.24,0:21:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別投訴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.66,0:21:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才沒時間跟你開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.41,0:21:04.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能源加強到90%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要避開阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.42,0:21:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動作快點阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.19,0:21:08.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,瞭解!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.73,0:21:19.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,高達隊脫離射程了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.62,0:21:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好,發射主炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.66,0:21:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼?這好像殖民地雷射炮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.46,0:22:02.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行,這樣下去會波及莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.93,0:22:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.31,0:22:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:09.16,0:22:10.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎麼了?捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.03,0:22:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.85,0:22:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,潛入亞古捷斯救回莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.94,0:22:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然後再回艦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.29,0:22:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行...你一個人去太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.47,0:22:26.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回來阿,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.46,0:22:28.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捷度!快回來!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.67,0:22:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一個人辦不了事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.10,0:22:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在没有道路的荒野里\N道もない荒れた原野に
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.10,0:22:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,建造铁路真是一件辛苦差事\Nレールを作るのは苦しいことさ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.10,0:23:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是\Nだけど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:07.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可以不知晓远方\N遠い向こうも知らなくちゃいけない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我们的路现在才开始\N僕達は これからなんだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.80,0:23:24.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人们都说我们是“忘记了梦想的小孩子”\N“夢を忘れた子供達”と 人は言う
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.50,0:23:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊啊 时代正在哭泣\Nああー 時代が泣いている
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.68,0:23:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們可不知道哈曼的亞古捷斯啥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.89,0:23:50.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是用強制手段就很簡單了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.73,0:23:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成功地侵入了亞古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.66,0:23:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是啥？ 奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.01,0:23:58.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,艾噗…艾噗… 波蕾？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.73,0:24:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為她似乎認識莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.43,0:24:02.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是想找她問話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.33,0:24:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下集 高達ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.67,0:24:06.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈曼的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.60,0:24:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,NEWTYPE們的相逢

